%html{html_attrs('en-US'), class: Rails.env}
  %head
    %title= @pagetitle.nil? ? "turkopticon - Mturk requester reviews" : "turkopticon : " + @pagetitle
    = stylesheet_link_tag 'generic'
    %meta{:name => "google-site-verification", :content => "UWLKIWNd0faYwT10vzkBZI5wvuQpuRtiEcZh9ZiMsBM"}
  %body
    #login_nav= render :partial => 'layouts/login_nav'
    = link_to content_tag(:div, nil, id: 'header'), controller: 'main', action: 'info'
    #nav= render :partial => 'layouts/nav'
    #content
      #flash_messages
        - if flash[:success]
          .success= flash[:success].html_safe
        - if flash[:notice]
          .notice= flash[:notice].html_safe
        - if flash[:warning]
          .warning= flash[:warning].html_safe
        - if flash[:error]
          .error= flash[:error].html_safe
      = yield
    #footer
      Comments, questions, issues? Please check the <a href='/faq/index.html'>frequently asked questions</a> page first. If your question isn't addressed there, please post to our discussion forum, #{link_to 'turkopticon-discuss', controller: 'forum', action: 'index'}. If you do not wish to post to the forum, you may email <a href="mailto:info@turkopticon.info">info@turkopticon.info</a>, but please note we may ask you to post it to the discussion list, <strong>or post it to the forum ourselves. Please be advised that there is no expectation of privacy for mail sent to <a href="mailto:info@turkopticon.info">info@turkopticon.info</a> or email sent to the personal addresses of any Turkopticon administrators regarding Turkopticon.</strong> Please also note that Turkopticon is a volunteer effort and that at any given time we are likely to have a large backlog of emails. We will do our best to reply to your email in a timely manner, but we can make no guarantees. Thank you for your patience.
      %br/
      %br/
      %br/
